comments: Finney-Smith (DAL) and Biyombo (PHX) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Paul (PHX) reaches in and makes contact with Porzingis' (DAL) body in the post and affects his SQBR.
Brunson (DAL) briefly grasps and releases Booker's (PHX) arm off-ball without affecting his ability to defend.
Biyombo (PHX) and Porzingis (DAL) engage and separate on the opposite side of the basket during the rebound.
Biyombo (PHX) does not establish himself in Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path when he delivers contact on the screen.
Booker (PHX) establishes himself in a legal guarding position during Doncic's (DAL) pass.

Replay review of the foul called on Booker (PHX) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful. Booker (PHX) maintains a legal guarding position as he blocks Finney-Smith's (DAL) driving shot attempt and absorbs the contact as Finney-Smith leads unnaturally with his off-arm.
Paul (PHX) and Finney-Smith (DAL) engage and disengage after the screen.
Porzingis (DAL) makes marginal contact with Crowder (PHX) on the perimeter.
Porzingis (DAL) makes marginal contact with Bridges (PHX) after Bridges passes the ball.
Porzingis (DAL) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
